quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"“Nûn. Ndikulumbilira cholembera (chimene akulembera angelo), ndi zimene amalemba"
  68,2,“Pa chisomo cha Mbuye wako iwe sindiwe wamisala (pokupatsa uneneri)
  68,3,"“Ndipo ndithu udzakhala ndi malipiro akulu osaduka, (onkerankera mtsogolo chifukwa cha mavuto amene ukukumana nawo pofikitsa uthenga)"
  68,4,“Ndipo ndithu uli nawo makhalidwe abwino kwambiri (omwe Allah adakulenga nawo)
  68,5,"“Basi, posachedwapa uona, iwonso aona"
  68,6,“Kuti ndani mwa inu wamisala (iwe kapena iwo)
  68,7,“Ndithu Mbuye wako akum’dziwa bwino amene wasokera panjira yake. Ndiponso akuwadziwa bwino amene ali oongoka
  68,8,"“Choncho, usawamvere otsutsa; (usasiye zimene uli nazo ngakhale sakugwirizana nazo)"
  68,9,“Akufuna kuti ukadakhala wofewa kwa iwo (pa zinthu zina) nawo akadakhala ofewa (kwa iwe)
  68,10,"“Ndipo usamumvere aliyense wochulukitsa kulumbira, woyaluka"
  68,11,"“Wojeda, woyenda ndi ukazitape (ndi cholinga choononga umodzi wawo)"
  68,12,"“Wotsekereza zabwino, wamtopola, wamachimo ambiri"
  68,13,“Wouma mtima; pamwamba pa izi ndi wodzipachika mu mtundu wa ena (pomwe iye sali m’menemo)
  68,14,“Chifukwa choti iye ndi mwini chuma ndi ana (ndi zimene ali kunyadira)
  68,15,"“Zikawerengedwa kwa iye Ayah Zathu amanena: “Izi ndi nthano za akale (ndi zabodza zawo, zopeka).”"
  68,16,“Timuika pamphuno pake chizindikiro (chosasiyana nacho kuti ayaluke nacho pamaso pa anthu)
  68,17,"“Ndithu ife tidawayesa (eni mzinda wa Makka ndi mtendere omwe udali pa iwo, koma adakana monga) momwe tidawayesera eni munda, pamene adalumbira kuti akathyola (zipatso za m’munda wawozo) mbandakucha (kuti osauka asawaone angawapemphe)"
  68,18,"“Ndipo sadapatule (ngakhale wosauka ndi m’modzi yemwe ponena kuti uje timpatse, uje tisampatse, kapena sadanene kuti: “Ngati Allah afuna).”"
  68,19,“Mliri woopsa wochokera kwa Mbuye wako udauzinga (mundawo nthawi yausiku) iwo ali mtulo
  68,20,“Choncho udakhala ngati wokololedwa (chifukwa cha mliri uja)
  68,21,“Tero adaitanizana nthawi ya mbandakucha
  68,22,““Lawilirani kumunda wanu kuja ngati mukufuna kukolola (kuopera kuti angakuoneni osauka).”
  68,23,“Adanyamuka uku akunong’ onezana
  68,24,"“(Akunena kuti): “Asakulowelereni wosauka lero mmenemo.”"
  68,25,“Ndipo adalawilira ali ndi chitsimikizo choti atha kuwamana (osauka)
  68,26,"“Choncho pamene adauona, adanena (uku akunjenjemera): “Ndithu ife tasokera (sikuno ayi, munda wathu uja siuno).”"
  68,27,"““Iyayi, ndiwomwewu; koma tamanidwa zinthu zake.”"
  68,28,"“Wolungama mwa iwo adanena: “Kodi sindinakuuzeni (pamene mudali kulangizana zomana osowa) kuti bwanji osamkumbukira Allah (ndi kusintha cholinga chanu)?”"
  68,29,"“(Iwo) adanena: “Alemekezeke Mbuye wathu ndithu ife tidali achinyengo (chifukwa cha kuipa kwa cholinga chathu).”"
  68,30,“Ndipo adatembenukirana ndikuyamba kudzudzulana
  68,31,"“Adati: “E chionongeko chathu! Ndithu Ife tidapyola malire (m’chinyengo chathu).”"
  68,32,““Mwina Mbuye wathu angatipatse zabwino m’malo mwa munda wathuwu. Ndithu ife tikufunitsitsa kwa Mbuye wathu (chikhululuko Chake).”
  68,33,"“Umo ndi mmene chimakhalira chilango (Changa chomwe ndimachitsitsa pa dziko lapansi kwa amene chamuyenera); koma chilango cha tsiku lachimaliziro nchachikulu zedi, akadakhala akudziwa"